<div class="app-hero">
  <div class="badge">✦ AI-Powered Tool</div>
  <h1>🌍 Travel AI Assistant</h1>
  <p>Your personal travel planner. Get destination picks, packing lists, itineraries, and travel tips.</p>
</div>

<div class="app-layout">
  <div class="sidebar">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Quick Prompts</h3>
      <button class="prompt-btn" onclick="usePrompt(this)"><span class="emoji">🏔️</span>Best destinations for hiking</button>
      <button class="prompt-btn" onclick="usePrompt(this)"><span class="emoji">🎒</span>5-day Europe packing list</button>
      <button class="prompt-btn" onclick="usePrompt(this)"><span class="emoji">💰</span>Budget travel tips for Asia</button>
      <button class="prompt-btn" onclick="usePrompt(this)"><span class="emoji">🌊</span>Top coastal road trips USA</button>
      <button class="prompt-btn" onclick="usePrompt(this)"><span class="emoji">🗓️</span>2-week Japan itinerary</button>
      <button class="prompt-btn" onclick="usePrompt(this)"><span class="emoji">🌿</span>Best national parks to visit</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Travel Mode</h3>
      <button class="mode-btn active" onclick="setMode('adventure', this)">🏕️ Adventure & Nature</button>
      <button class="mode-btn" onclick="setMode('culture', this)">🏛️ Culture & History</button>
      <button class="mode-btn" onclick="setMode('budget', this)">💸 Budget Traveler</button>
      <button class="mode-btn" onclick="setMode('luxury', this)">✨ Luxury & Comfort</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chat-area">
    <div class="messages" id="messages">
      <div class="message ai">
        <div class="avatar ai">🌿</div>
        <div class="bubble">
          <span class="ai-label">Travel AI</span>
          Hey there, adventurer! 🌍 I'm your AI travel assistant. Whether you're planning a backpacking trip through Patagonia, a budget euro trip, or just looking for your next national park — I'm here to help.<br><br>
          Ask me anything: destination ideas, packing lists, itineraries, cultural tips, or budget hacks. What's your next adventure?
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="input-area">
      <textarea id="userInput" placeholder="Ask about destinations, packing, itineraries..." rows="1"
        onkeydown="handleKey(event)" oninput="autoResize(this)"></textarea>
      <button class="send-btn" id="sendBtn" onclick="sendMessage()">Send ✈️</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  Part of <a href="index.html">Merrill Kersey's Portfolio</a> &mdash;
  <a href="scratch.html">Travel & Nature</a> &mdash;
  <a href="resume.html">Résumé</a>
</footer>

